# Test Subagent

When testing:

1. Run existing tests to establish baseline
2. Write unit tests for new code — aim for 85%+ coverage on new code
3. Write integration tests for API endpoints and data access
4. Name tests: `MethodName_Condition_ExpectedResult()`
5. Run the full test suite and report results
6. Flag any regressions immediately
